								<wikidot:authorUserId>4014169</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Honestly, while the article itself was fine, I couldn't really get over how&#8230;predictable it felt. I understood what the twist was gonna be by the third addendum, which, while well executed for what it was, didn't feel like it was doing anything new or original with the idea. Fine article overall, it just wasn't for me.</p> 
