					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7759607#post-4024818</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7759607/scp-4024#post-4024818</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 15 Oct 2018 14:26:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>hillo315</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2737917</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So it's a reverse <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4040">Sloth's Pit</a>. Fascinating.</p> <blockquote> <p>“It does not matter,” croaked the old wizard. “Our mission is more important. You must find <strong>S</strong>ullivan <strong>C</strong>ornelius <strong>P</strong>endragon of the <strong>Forty Third</strong> Chamber, and you must tell him…”</p> </blockquote> <p>Neat insight into the anomaly's inner workings.<br /> +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7759607#post-4020408</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7759607/scp-4024#post-4020408</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 10 Oct 2018 21:52:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TheMightyMcB</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4483018</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Interesting take on the whole &quot;narrative SCP&quot; thing. Not overly narmy, and the article manages to pull off having multiple effects across different media by relating them all back to the nebulous narrative-based dimension. There are a few details that come off as Checkhov's guns (namely the Buddhist temple), but I liked it overall. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
